      </h1>

      <p class="mb-6 text-base">       
       I believe technology is a means to an end—not the starting point.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-6 text-base">
        I help startups and teams clarify the problem they’re 
        solving and then design and build solutions that actually deliver results.
        
      </p>

       <p class="mb-6 text-base">
